precis:
Amendments to the CORRECTIONS AND CONDITIONAL RELEASE REGULATIONS which
enable the Correctional Service of Canada to implement the provisions
contained in Bill C-45 with respect to deductions for room and board and
to the requirements for the National Parole Board to conduct reviews
within established time frames.
